    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Particulars of the place where a person, organization, building, or monument can be found on a street or other thoroughfare; typically consisting of a number, street name, the name of the administrative area (a town or district). May also include a postcode, as the street address may also be the "mailing address."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
